Detailed Description

cvmx_mix::_irhwm

MIX_IRHWM = MIX I-Ring High-Water Mark Threshold Register

Description: NOTE: To write to the MIX_IHWM register, a device would issue an IOBST directed at the MIO. To read the MIX_IHWM register, a device would issue an IOBLD64 directed at the MIO.
